# Immigration Lawyer Domain Rules

When modifying this codebase:

- AI prompts and agents must never guarantee visa approval or invent client facts
- All AI-generated content requires lawyer review before client or Home Affairs use
- Use `[NEEDS CLIENT INPUT]` for missing information in drafts
- Validate user input with Zod at API boundaries
- Enforce case access via `userHasCaseAccess()` — never trust client-provided caseId alone
- Dev Auth (`AUTH_MODE=dev`) is for local development only
- Australian English for all user-facing legal document output
